01:26:15,333 --> 01:26:16,500
Stop, stop, stop, stop.

1998
01:26:16,583 --> 01:26:18,458
Maddie, I love you.

1999
01:26:18,541 --> 01:26:19,916
You're like, I guess,

2000
01:26:20,000 --> 01:26:22,583
-a great-granddaughter to me
